metadata.name: The lake fairy
metadata.description:
Hi everyone! I'm glad to introduce a new separate world from the angels, and it will be the world of lake fairies or nymphs. Their Familiars are frogs, and each nymph has her magic Familiar, that magical theriomorphic spirit, according to medieval Western European beliefs, which served witches, sorcerers and other practitioners of magic.
For them, frogs are a kind of deity, so they honor them by dedicating paintings, sculptures, architectural elements, and the royal couple of nymphs are part-time Priests, whose Familiars are the strongest frogs.
I used colors associated with frogs and algae (green) and complimentary pink, which refers to the lotusâ€¦
